Zack & Quack's Pop-Up Circus / Pop-Up Monster Zack wants to tame the wildest animal alive, and goes to the circus. When Quack pops-up a dinosaur, they run into Jurassic-sized problems.
When a fuzzy baby monster pops up in the garden, Zack and his friends head off to reunite it with its mama (2013).
